import React from 'react'
import {Grid} from '@material-ui/core'
import Posttemplate from './Posttemplate'



function Posts() {
    
    return (
         <>
         <Grid item lg={3} sm={6} xs={12}>
            <Posttemplate/>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item lg={3} sm={4} xs={12}>
          <Posttemplate/>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item lg={3} sm={4} xs={12}>
        <Posttemplate/>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item lg={3} sm={4} xs={12}>
      <Posttemplate/>
    </Grid>
    </>   
                  
    )
}

export default Posts
